race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Hcp (C4)
race.comment: PURR SEFANEE (8) seeks the hat-trick off easy front-running wins (wide gates) at Hobart and Devonport over this distance. She keeps getting better and jumps from the inside barrier today. Stays down in the weights and she rates to go on with the job. ONLY OLD ONCE (7) peaks and the former Victorian found more like her best placing here over 1400m behind Kakia. She's won over a mile and should be right in it. SUGOI LEGEND (1) always puts in and would be a hope putting his best foot forward. MILES 'N' MILES (6) settled last and didn't do a bad job first-up in the same contest. At his best over middle distances, but this trip suits better now and he maps to be around the mark.
